# Frontend Environment Configuration — Render Static Site
# ============================================================
# When deploying on Render, this value is automatically injected
# by render.yaml via the fromService block. You do NOT need to set
# this manually in the Render dashboard.
#
# For local development, create a .env.local file and set:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080

# For production (Render will inject this automatically):
# VITE_API_URL=https://ems-backend.onrender.com
